<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">听说古文字中的<delay8 />象形文字，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />通过研究线索的雕塑<delay8 />
已经可以解读出来了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到研究者的热情，<delay8 />
我心里就不禁激动起来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">飘扬流畅的衣料褶纹<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生动地呈现出迎风而立的形象～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />实在是太精妙了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />英挺的雕塑<delay20 />被设计成
从下往上看时<delay8 />
最能体会到它的美～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这就是传闻中那幅有名的名画啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是神秘的微笑～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画不可思议地让人感到一阵暖风～<10_4 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里暖气特别足<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />应该不是这个原因吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />惊人的名画的厉害之处<delay20 />
在于它的跃动感～<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令人不禁想鼓励一句，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“工作要加油啊”。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正中间那一位是公主吧！<delay frames="40" />
然后左边的人是画家<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是在画什么画呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果说是在画公主，
画的就会是公主的背影<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
唔～<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有点神秘呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">所谓的美术<delay20 />并不光是
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />去描绘看上去美丽的事物。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着这幅名贵的名画，
我很能领会这个道理。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着这幅沉没的名画，<delay20 />
明明画中的场景极尽哀伤，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我却不禁认为它<delay20 />美得摄人心魂。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">神秘的名画的氛围<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />稍微有些可怕，<delay8 />
却不知为何令人移不开眼呢～
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好<tag a="110" b="33" />
不是<delay8 />这种气氛。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />仔细一看这幅画，<delay20 />每一笔都是点状的。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我也喜欢精细的工作，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我大概做不到如此细致<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">闪烁的名画中天空的表现方式<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太巧妙了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就想不到能这样呈现。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />磅礴的名画中的<delay8 />巨浪
动感十足！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想出如此大胆的构图的人，<delay20 />
想必性格也十分大胆吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />武士的雕刻<delay8 />
看起来就像在守卫这间展览室一样。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是可靠！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />远古的雕塑的这身形！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这全身的纹路！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有<delay8 />绝对不会忽视的眼睛的部分！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然不知道这么说合不合适，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但这实在是太可爱了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是看着这座<delay8 />似曾相识的雕塑，<delay20 />
就能让人不禁展开思考。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请问<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />这个的捐赠人
是<tag a="110" b="4" />你吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了我们<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感谢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>